{"word":"G316 - ἀναγκαῖος - anankaîos - an-ang-kah'-yos - Near","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀναγκαῖος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">anankaîos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-ang-kah'-yos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Near</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"தேவையானது"},{"paragraph":"what one cannot do without, indispensable"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G318 - ἀνάγκη - anánkē - an-ang-kay'/318\">G318</a>; <i>necessary</i>; by implication <i>close</i> (of kin): - near, necessary, necessity, needful.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}